63&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Canadian+Journal+of+Public+Health&amp;title=Accountability+in+public+health+units:+using+a+modified+nominal+group+technique+to+develop+a+balanced+scorecard+for+performance+measurement&quot;&amp;author=VA+Robinson&amp;author=D+Hunter&amp;author=S+Shortt&amp;volume=94&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;pages=391-96&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2684743&amp;issue-id=175724&amp;journal-id=63&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></li><li id="B11"><span class="citation">York Region Community Health Services, Public Health Branch 2007 Balanced Scorecard <a href="http://www.york.ca/Publications/Default+Economic+Publications.htm" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" ref="reftype=extlink&amp;article-id=2684743&amp;issue-id=175724&amp;journal-id=63&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=External%7CLink%7CURI" target="_blank">http://www.york.ca/Publications/Default+Economic+Publications.htm</a></span></li><li id="B12"><span class="citation">Statistics Canada Health Regions and Peer Groups <a href="http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/82-221-x/01103/4062628-eng.htm" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" ref="reftype=extlink&amp;article-id=2684743&amp;issue-id=175724&amp;journal-id=63&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=External%7CLink%7CURI" target="_blank">http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/82-221-x/01103/4062628-eng.htm</a></span></li></ul></div></div></div><!--post-content--><div class="courtesy-note whole_rhythm small"><hr />Articles from <span class="acknowledgment-journal-title">BMC Public Health</span> are provided here courtesy of <strong>BioMed Central</strong></div></div>\n            \n            \n        \n            \n        </div>\n        <!-- Book content -->\n    </div>\n    \n    <div id="rightcolumn" class="four_col co